%h1
  Contact us
  %small We would love to hear from you!
%p.text-warning Please fill out this form and we will get in touch with you shortly.
= simple_form_for @contact do |f|
  = f.input :name
  = f.input :email
  = f.input :message, as: :text, input_html: { rows: 10 }
  .form-actions
    = f.submit 'Send', class: 'btn btn-primary'

.span7
  %p Comments, barks, emails, tweets, meows,  posts, circles – however you want to connect with us is just fine.
